Smallholdings_desc.en_US: Enables converting Burgage Plots (Lv1) with Backyard Extensions into Smallholdings. Like Artisans, Smallholding Families treat their backyards as a permanent job, increasing their Yield.

IncreasedExportValueMinorTrades.en_US: Increased Export Price on Minor Trades

IncreasedExportValueMinorTrades_desc.en_US: All Minor Trades base Export Value is increased by +50%.

UnlockKennelsAndDogs_desc.en_US: Enables ordering a Hunting Hound for the Hunting Camp. Hunting Hounds provide +1 Small Game every 7 days.

ForagedGoodsCapacityBoost.en_US: Increased Capacity for Foraged Goods Deposits

ForagedGoodsCapacityBoost_desc.en_US: Wild Berries and Mushroom Deposits have doubled capacity.

TitheApprovalPenalty_desc.en_US: Enabling the <h>Tithe</> causes a loss of <h>Approval</> similar to <h>Land Tax</>.

IncreasedForesterSuccessRate.en_US: Increased Success Chance for Tree Planting

IncreasedForesterSuccessRate_desc.en_US: The base chance of failure (50%) when planting <h>Trees</> no longer applies.

SkilledWoodworkers_desc.en_US: Bowyers and Joiners Efficiency: +20%. Warbows, Crossbows, Small Shields and Large Shields Export Value: +20%.

IncreasedPassiveIncome.en_US: Increased Regional Wealth from Burgage Plots

IncreasedPassiveIncome_desc.en_US: All occupied Burgage Plots produce +1 Regional Wealth per month.

CheaperBurgageUpgrades_desc.en_US: Upgrading a Burgage Plot to the next Level requires half the Construction Materials and any Regional Wealth cost is removed.

SaltAndIronImportDiscount.en_US: Salt & Iron Ore Import Value reduction

LivestockYieldPenalty_desc.en_US: Backyard Animal Pens, Chicken Coops and Pastures Efficiency: -20%.

MilitiaEquipmentApprovalGain_desc.en_US: Gain a small amount of Approval for each Militia Footmen or Militia Spear Unit at full strength and with their necessary equipment ready.

ImprovedStonemasonsStation_desc.en_US: Stone Gatherer Camp Labor Speed: +30% and Stone Mason's Station Efficiency: +30%.

HuntingAndFishingProductivityPenalty.en_US: Decreased Labor Speed for Hunting and Fishing

HuntingAndFishingProductivityPenalty_des.en_US: Labor Speed for Hunting Camp and Fisherman's Hut: -20%.

OxHandlerSpeedBuff_desc.en_US: Ox Handlers and their Oxen move with +10% increased speed when assigned to Hitching Posts or Stables.

ArmorerArtisanBuff_desc.en_US: Armorer Efficiency: +20%. Helmets, Mail Armor & Plate Armor Export Value: +20%.

ImprovedMineMaintenance_desc.en_US: Proximity of <h>Mines</> are no longer a factor for <h>Collapse Chance</>. <h>Maintenance</> duration of all <h>Mines</>: +30%.

MiningTradeDiscounts_desc.en_US: Trade Routes for Iron Ore and Salt are free to establish. Iron Ore and Salt Import Value: -30%.

LivestockImportDiscounts_desc.en_US: All Animals (Oxen, Mules, Horses, Sheep, Lambs, Goat, Pigs, Chickens) Import Price: -20%.

ResilientSheep_desc.en_US: <h>Sheep</> no longer die at <h>High Elevation</> during Winter months.

FertilityBonus_desc.en_US: All fields in this region gain a Fertility bonus for each different crop in the region

ForestArcherBonus_desc.en_US: Archers gain a major damage bonus in forests

BackyardAgricultureBonus_desc.en_US: Animal Husbandry and Backyard Agriculture has a higher yield

Lv1BurgagePlotBuff_desc.en_US: Living in a Lv1 Burgage Plot applies a small amount of bonus passive <h>APPROVAL</> per family

DoubleStallStorage_Desc.en_US: Double the storage size in each stall

ZweibackProduction_desc.en_US: Enables the production of Zweiback in Bakeries, a more durable, spoil resistant form of bread.

SmokedFishProduction_desc.en_US: Enables the production of Smoked Fish by combining Fish and Salt.

WinterFishing_desc.en_US: Fishermen are able to fish during the Winter

RegionMoraleBoost_desc.en_US: Troops in this Region will fight with improved Morale

FlatRegionApprovalBuff_desc.en_US: All <h>Families</> in this region provide a small amount of passive <h>Approval</>

ApprovalAndInfluenceFromCombatDeaths_des.en_US: This region will recieve <h>APPROVAL</> and <h>INFLUENCE</> for every foreign troop defeated on it's soil

Lv1BurgagePlotWealthBuff.en_US: Increase Lvl1 Burgage Plot Wealth Generation

Lv1BurgagePlotWealthBuff_desc.en_US: Lvl1 Burgage Plots generate an increased amount of passive wealth

BackyardAgricultureNerf_desc.en_US: Decrease the amount of goods produced from backyard crops, orchards and animal pens

CheaperLv2BurgagePlots_desc.en_US: Cost to upgrade to Lv2 Burgage Plots is drastically reduced

ImprovedUpHillSpeed_desc.en_US: Decrease the uphill walk penalty for animals and villagers in this region

IncreasedMoveSpeed.en_US: Increase villager and animal walk speed

IncreasedMoveSpeed_desc.en_US: Villager and animals in this region walk marginally faster

DecreasedApprovalLossFromTaxation_desc.en_US: Decrease the amount of Approval lost by means of Taxation

IncreaseBasicItemPrices_desc.en_US: Increase the trade prices of basic, Minor trade items

DecreasedLoggerSpeed_desc.en_US: Increase the time taken to turn TIMBER into PLANKS

IncreasedPlowSpeed_desc.en_US: Increase the speed at which plants are tilled by means of manual plowing

DecreasedRaiderBribaryCost_desc.en_US: Decrease the cost of bribing an attacking force

IncreaseRegionWealthFromTrade.en_US: Increased Region Wealth generation from Trade

IncreaseRegionWealthFromTrade_desc.en_US: Increase the amount of Regional Wealth generation from trade

DecreasedDeepMineCollapseChance_desc.en_US: Decrease the chance of deep mine collapsing when multiple mines are within a radius of one another

ReduceMineUpkeep_desc.en_US: Decrease the rate in which supplies are needed for maintenance.

MeadProduction_desc.en_US: Enables the production of Mead in brewerys.

LebkuchenProduction_desc.en_US: Enables the production of Lebkuchen in bakeries. A form of bread.

CiderProduction_desc.en_US: Enabled the production of Cider in breweries. A form of drink for the Tavern

AdditionalPollinationBonus_desc.en_US: Apiaries provide an additional pollination bonus to Berries and Orchards in this region.

TradeRoutesImprovesApproval_desc.en_US: Approval is gained from each dedicated Trade Route

GainInfluenceFromTrading_desc.en_US: The flourishing market and its profits have not gone unnoticed in the empire and put you in a more favorable negotiating position. But be warned, your rule is not set in stone.

IncreaseImmigrationRate_Desc.en_US: Increase the rate at which families move into empty homes

ForagingHutSupportsExtraFamilies_desc.en_US: Extra families able to inhabit foraging huts when perk is active.

PasturesGainAnElevationBonus_desc.en_US: This is the value for how much more sheep yield you will receive when the New Horizon perk is active, also removes the risk of sheep dying in winter months.

InterestOnRegionalWealth_desc.en_US: Increase regional wealth on a monthly basics by a percentage increase with the market rights perk active.

GainInfluenceFromRegionalWealth_desc.en_US: After spending Regional Wealth, gain Influence equal to a proportion of its cost

BurgagePlotProduceMoreRegionalWealthWhen.en_US: Burgage Plot Produce More Regional Wealth When Approval Is High
Your rule is not taken for granted, but means daily negotiations with your subjects. Stable and prospective times are only possible if they are satisfied with you as their ruler.

ProficiencyApprovalBuff_Desc.en_US: Gain a flat amount of Proficiency in all buildings, that decays as you get further away from 50% approval

CombatHillEffectiveness_desc.en_US: Soldiers from this region go uphill faster, and gain a damage bonus when fighting on a hill.

DoubleMushroomCapacity_Desc.en_US: Double the amount of mushrooms avaliable in each clump

RuralBuildingProficiencyBuff_Desc.en_US: Rural Buildings gain a flat amount of Proficiency

EfficiencyFromCraftsmanNetwork_Desc.en_US: Industries in this Region gain efficiency for each adjacent Region with a settlement level of 3 or lower

CraftmenWithFilledAdditionalLivingSpaceO.en_US: Craftmen With Filled Additional Living Space Operate With Extra Proficiency
Extra Proficiency given to craftsmen with filled additional living space and work in the same building.

BuildingsNearRiverGainRegionWealth.en_US: Buildings Near River Gain Region Wealth

BuildingsNearRiverGainRegionWealth_desc.en_US: Region wealth generation increased for all buildings close to rivers.

RegionalWealthGainedFromChurch_desc.en_US: Region wealth is gained from having a church in your region. The higher level the church, the more regional wealth this will generate.

UpgradeBurgagePlotsToTier1Industries.en_US: Upgrade Burgage Plots To Tier-1 Industries

UpgradeBurgagePlotsToTier1Industries_des.en_US: Burgage plots can be upgraded into dedicated tier-1 industries (vegetable patches, chicken coops, etc)

TenPercentTaxIncrease_desc.en_US: -10% decrease to regional wealth when perk is active.

TenPercentRegionWealthDecrease_desc.en_US: +10% increase to tax when perk is active.

CraftsmenDoNotRequireAnyChurchLevel.en_US: Craftsmen Do Not Require Any Church Level

CraftsmenDoNotRequireAnyChurchLevel_desc.en_US: Craftsmen do not require any Church level but -25% Influence from this settlement.

RawResourcesPriceDeducation_desc.en_US: Raw resources (iron, leather, berries, etc) are paid for with 50% of the usual Regional Wealth cost

DoubleBerryCapacity_desc.en_US: Double the amount of berries avaliable in each clump

ForestersPlantTreesAllYearRound.en_US: Foresters Plant Trees All Year Round

ForestersPlantTreesAllYearRound_desc.en_US: Foresters can plant trees all year round.
